# 🌿 MILO

MILO is a static website built using **HTML and CSS** that acts as a digital bridge between local Indian businesses and customers. It focuses on helping small artisans, craftsmen, and service providers gain online visibility and grow their reach through a clean and simple user interface.

---

## 📌 About the Project

MILO is designed as a multi-page static website that simulates a real-world local business discovery platform. It connects rural and urban Indian small businesses with customers, allowing users to explore services, learn about the platform, and discover extended offerings in a structured way.

The website is divided into multiple pages to improve navigation and clarity.

---

## 🏠 Home Page (Index)

- Acts as the landing page of MILO  
- Includes a search bar for discovering services and businesses  
- Provides login / signup UI (front-end only)  
- Gives quick navigation to all main pages  
- Displays key highlights of the platform in a clean layout  

---

## ℹ️ About Page

- Explains the purpose and vision of MILO  
- Describes how MILO supports local artisans, craftsmen, and small businesses  
- Highlights the goal of bridging rural and urban India digitally  
- Builds trust and understanding for users visiting the platform  

---

## 🛍️ Services Page

- Showcases main categories of services available on the platform  
- Helps users explore different types of businesses easily  
- Designed with simple cards or sections for better readability  
- Focuses on core offerings like:
  - Local shops  
  - Handicrafts  
  - Home services  
  - Small business listings  

---

## 🚀 Extended Services Page

- Provides deeper and more detailed service categories  
- Includes additional or premium-level services beyond basic listings  
- Helps users explore niche or specialized business categories  
- Designed for better scalability of the platform in future updates  
- Acts as an advanced discovery section for users  

---

## ✨ Features

- Clean and minimal UI design  
- Multi-page website structure  
- Search bar UI for business discovery  
- Login / Sign up interface (frontend only)  
- Organized service-based navigation  
- Responsive layout (basic level)

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- HTML5  
- CSS3  

---

## 🎯 Objective

The main objective of MILO is to digitally empower local Indian businesses by providing a simple and accessible platform where customers can discover services, artisans, and small enterprises from across India.

